Job Description
Primary Duties and Responsibilities:
- Responsible for providing the company's after-sales technical and services support
- Provide technical expertise for required solutions
- Assist in product roll-out and startup, maintain current equipment and resolve faults as required
- Ensure 24x7 standby services through a rotational duty schedule
- May provide supports in a pre-sale through post-sale capacity.
Job Requirements
Background / Experience Required:
- UPS (Uninterruptible Power Supply) servicing, commissioning and troubleshooting
- Technical background in analyzing electrical problem Knowledge in the UPS architecture and electrical single line diagram (SLD)
- Willing to work under hard deadlines and pressure
- Attend ad-hoc jobs and service calls
- Team player and hard-working Customer-oriented.